- Winter land
- Djungle land
- Underwater world

snippet.title: Ipic Play – Kids Find Fun at Ipic Play – Cape Town’s Newest Indoor Playground For Kids (Episode 13)
snippet.description:
Kids Find Fun – fun videos for kids! In our 13th episode we visited Ipic Play, Cape Town’s newest Indoor Adventure Playground for kids, situated in the suburb of Durbanville, Cape Town, South Africa.

Ipic Play has endless action for the kids – Here’s what to expect:
• Jump Zone
• Clip and Climb Zone
• Extreme Obstacle Challenge
• Walk in the Clouds
• Giant Slides
• Ball Blaster Tower
• Gladiator Pit
• Toddler Town
• Digital Media Room

The bright colorful equipment, high ceilings, great lighting and cleanliness creates a wonderfully refreshing space conducive to fast-paced and fun exploration for the kids. There is also a Knead Bakery and a Gym! Plenty to keep the parents occupied too.

The staff were engaging, friendly and helpful. Thanks Ipic Play for the FUN!

We hope you enjoyed our adventure as much as we did! Leave a comment for us and don’t forget to subscribe to our channel to watch more videos of us finding fun in South Africa – https://www.youtube.com/c/kidsfindfun

snippet.title: Indoor Playground Family Fun for Kids at Andy's Lekland
snippet.description:
Come along and play with Family Playlab, this time at Andy's lekland in Nacka, outside Stockholm, Sweden.

When we played at Andy's lekland in Nacka, it became quite clear that we are spoiled with the much larger play centers that we are used to. The playground in Nacka was small and packed with kids in a cramped space and very, very noisy.

Let's just say that we weren't impressed :)

But we rode the slides and jumped in the trampolines and climbed around and had a fun time anyway.

This is basically the same concept as Busfabriken and Leo's lekland.

Indoor playground family fun for kids.
